    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                <pb facs="nei.j4b.2.34-35"/>
                <note type="curatorial">34</note>
                <note type="curatorial">Neihardt Collection</note>
                
                <opener>
                    
                    <dateline>
                        Nov. 18. 1921
                    </dateline>
                    
                    <salute>Dear Daddy-</salute>
                    
                </opener>
                
                <p>I hope you are feeling well. We got those <unclear/> from cousin mary they are very good I hope you will be home before long it will not be very long now. 
                The boys in school tease me about my name they call me a pig because my name is Sig.</p> 
                <p>I have Aubrey Bennett a good hard punch in the jaws for calling me a pig and made them ache But that did</p>
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4b.2.34-35"/>
                <note type="curatorial">35</note>
                
                <p>not do any good. I wish you would tell me how to fight the Boys because they call me a pig all the time and I do not no how to manage it. 
                because every time I do anything why it makes it worse. I shoked him once and made him quit for a while. I hope you are not sick before you come back</p> 
                <closer>
                    <salute>Love and best hugs</salute> 
                    <signed>Sigurd</signed>
                </closer>
                
            </div1>
            
        </body>
        
